{
  "stem": "19055.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 338.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the soldiers who were in active fighting unit were taking a chocolate Hershey bars from their pockets and throwing it to us, and cigarettes, and, and whatever they had-- chewing gum and canned food, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as good as they could be under the circumstances, as wonderful as they, they could be.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they really were to us the saviors and the angels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Soon, a, a major whose name was Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Julius Rock-- R-O-C-K-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] who was a medical officer in the unit-- and this [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] unit belonged to the 30th Infantry unit of the 9th Army.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rock ordered to evacuate a town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The name was Hillersleben.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this whole area is near [INAUDIBLE], Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He evacuated this town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Under threat, the mayor complied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put up us-- us up in that town, one or two, two families in a, in a home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you can imagine what it meant to a home, to sleep in a bed, to, to eat some food that, that it was human, that was edible.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The American army also set up a field hospital, I think for 1,000 beds, that I was immediately hospitalized and diagnosed as bilateral tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had TB in both of my lungs with pleurisy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's why the stabbing pains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] in, in itself, this is a death sentence in 1945, because there was no cure for tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I was treated by German doctors also, who were forced by the, by the Americans to treat us and take care of us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The American soldiers would come and visit us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we made acquaintance with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
